  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 350°F.",
    "In a pan, heat oil over medium heat. Add cumin seeds and sauté until they turn golden brown.",
    "Add onion and garlic; sauté for about 4-5 minutes until soft.",
    "Stir in ginger, coriander powder, nutmeg, oignon, salt, and curry leaves. Cook for an additional minute.",
    "Transfer the mixture to a blender and add lentils. Blend smoothly.",
    "Pour the blended mixture into an oven-safe dish. Bake in preheated oven for 30 minutes or until golden brown on top.",
    "Serve warm as a snack."
